query:
SELECT s.id as session_id, s.status, DATE(s.scheduledAt) as date, wl.id as workout_log_id 
FROM sessions s 
LEFT JOIN workout_logs wl ON wl.sessionId = s.id 
WHERE s.status = 'completed' 
ORDER BY s.scheduledAt DESC;
